<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Details Page</title>
    <style>
        /* General Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg,
                    #d4e157,
                    #aed581,
                    #81c784,
                    #4caf50,
                    #388e3c);
            background-size: 200% 200%;
            animation: gradientShift 10s ease infinite;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        @keyframes gradientShift {
            0% {
                background-position: 0% 50%;
            }

            50% {
                background-position: 100% 50%;
            }

            100% {
                background-position: 0% 50%;
            }
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-out forwards;
        }

        /* Title Section */
        .title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: slideDown 1.5s ease-out 0.3s forwards;
        }

        .title h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2e8b57;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #2e8b57, #74c69d);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .title h1:hover {
            color: #74c69d;
        }

        .title h1::before,
        .title h1::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            height: 4px;
            width: 40px;
            background-color: #2e8b57;
            border-radius: 2px;
            bottom: -10px;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .title h1::before {
            left: 0;
        }

        .title h1::after {
            right: 0;
        }

        /* Abstract and Motivation Containers */
        .abstract-container,
        .motivation-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f7faf7;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-out forwards;
            animation-delay: 0.5s;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .abstract-container:hover,
        .motivation-container:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        /* Text Sections */
        .abstract-text,
        .motivation-text {
            flex: 3;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .abstract-text h2,
        .motivation-text h2 {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            color: #2e8b57;
            font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: capitalize;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-style: italic;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #2e8b57, #74c69d);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #74c69d;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            text-align: left;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            position: relative;
            animation: popIn 0.6s ease-out 0.7s forwards;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        /* Image Sections */
        .abstract-img,
        .motivation-image {
            flex: 2;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transform: scale(0.9);
            opacity: 0;
            animation: zoomIn 1s ease-out 0.8s forwards;
        }

        .abstract-img img,
        .motivation-image img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 250px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .abstract-img img:hover,
        .motivation-image img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1) rotate(2deg);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* Paragraph Styling */
        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: left;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #666;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes popIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.9);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        @keyframes zoomIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.8);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {

            .abstract-container,
            .motivation-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .abstract-img,
            .motivation-image {
                margin-top: 15px;
            }

            .title h1 {
                font-size: 2.2em;
            }
        }
    </style>

</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Title Section -->
        <div class="title">
            <h1>Details</h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Abstract Section -->
        <div class="abstract-container">
            <div class="abstract-text">
                <h2>Abstract</h2>
                <p>
                    This research aims to address the pressing need for sustainable and
                    economically viable practices within the realm of large-scale event
                    planning. By leveraging advanced technological frameworks,
                    specifically Multi-Objective Optimization (MOO), we seek to
                    reconcile the often-conflicting objectives of reducing greenhouse
                    gas emissions and managing costs effectively. MOO will serve as a
                    guiding mechanism, enabling the identification of optimal solutions
                    that balance environmental impact and economic considerations.
                    Through a comprehensive analysis of various event planning factors,
                    including venue selection, transportation, waste management, and
                    energy consumption, we will develop a framework to assist event
                    organizers in making informed decisions that contribute to a more
                    sustainable future.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="abstract-img">
                <img src="./img1.jpg" alt="Environmental Impact Image 1" />
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Motivation Section -->
        <div class="motivation-container">
            <div class="motivation-text">
                <h2>Research Motivation</h2>
                <p>
                    Our event planning website tackles climate change and socioeconomic
                    inequality by offering affordable, low-carbon event options. It
                    empowers users to make budget-friendly and eco-conscious choices,
                    reducing significant carbon footprints often associated with events.
                    The app highlights venues with lower environmental impacts, making
                    sustainable choices accessible and easy. Additionally, it educates
                    users on the CO2 impact of their decisions, promoting environmental
                    awareness. By leveraging machine learning, the app personalizes
                    recommendations while aligning with low-carbon goals. Ultimately,
                    this platform merges environmental responsibility, social equity,
                    and technology, aiming to inspire a cultural shift toward
                    sustainable, affordable event planning.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="motivation-image">
                <img src="./img2.jpg" alt="Environmental Impact Image 2" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>